  "title": "tiler",
  "description": "<ul><li>Inspect and clean the interior and exterior walls floors and other other paving surfaces of the building, remove old tiles and complete the foundation treatment before paving.</li><li>Study the building construction drawings, accurately measure and mark the paving area,and plan the tile layout plan.</li><li>Lay all kinds of tiles and use tools to ensure that the tiles are aligned, the surface is flat, and the gaps are uniform.</li><li>Wipe out excess caulk and polish the paving surface to ensure that the work meets the standards.</li><li>Deal with problems during the process, check and replace the loose tiles in time after the process.</li><li>Cooperate with the construction team to complete the project schedule and obey the work arrangement.</li></ul>",
